Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.00,0:00:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,-3月25日-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.53,0:00:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,请用\N谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.47,0:00:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.44,0:00:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.65,0:00:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,老公 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.65,0:00:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我会努力存钱买房子的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.06,0:00:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我也去工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.23,0:00:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经讨论过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.53,0:00:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,有个好消息唷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.80,0:00:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,野上部长要调来我们公司
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.87,0:01:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,有来参加我们婚礼那个？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.24,0:01:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他一直很看好我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.91,0:01:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,说不定可以靠他升官唷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.52,0:01:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.39,0:01:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我被老公的上司侵犯了7天\N最后失去理性
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.43,0:01:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-3月31日-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.59,0:01:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,好重
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.99,0:01:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.03,0:02:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 害你要打扫\N没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.07,0:02:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好想喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.38,0:02:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,结束后来喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.85,0:02:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我去扫那边
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.49,0:02:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这个吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.60,0:02:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,都是碗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.72,0:02:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这放这？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.26,0:03:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,应该是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.96,0:03:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.67,0:03:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.27,0:03:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,真是个好房子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.18,0:03:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是公司的房子啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.95,0:03:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是借住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.82,0:03:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,单身赴任真辛苫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.69,0:03:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,雇个管家比较好唷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.06,0:03:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不过工作很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.83,0:03:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不想家里一直有外人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.68,0:03:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那拜托我太太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.25,0:04:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你太太是很会打扫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.35,0:04:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,可是这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.99,0:04:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,太麻烦她了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.73,0:04:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,没有的事 她也在找打工
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.17,0:04:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这样很打扰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.71,0:04:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,今天你打扫的很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.18,0:04:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,可以的话就麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.88,0:04:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.89,0:04:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,干杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.42,0:04:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.76,0:04:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-4月1日-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.83,0:05:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎回家 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.23,0:05:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,忘了东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.97,0:06:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.25,0:06:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你的手怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.62,0:06:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好冰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.19,0:06:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,喝个茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.19,0:06:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.46,0:07:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.50,0:07:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.27,0:07:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,害你这么麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.67,0:07:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不会的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.78,0:07:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这是身为太太该做的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.02,0:07:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.55,0:07:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,太太该做的不是这些
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.79,0:07:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,煮饭跟家事怎样都好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.63,0:07:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,真的太太该做的是别的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.85,0:07:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,部长 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.15,0:07:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你太性感了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.89,0:08:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,害我忍不住
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.29,0:08:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,变这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.23,0:08:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.53,0:08:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.87,0:08:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吧\N说什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.51,0:08:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我有老公了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.61,0:08:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.08,0:08:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.02,0:08:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这么不想要？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.83,0:08:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不想要！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.90,0:08:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,为了老公 别反抗我的好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.60,0:08:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.41,0:08:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你老公可以升官
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.91,0:08:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,都靠我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.08,0:08:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,希望他还有工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.15,0:09:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,最好听话唷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.77,0:09:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.67,0:09:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.43,0:09:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.84,0:09:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.75,0:10:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.36,0:10:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,乖一点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.13,0:10:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.77,0:11:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好色唷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.48,0:11:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.52,0:11:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.52,0:11:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.24,0:12:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.20,0:13:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.17,0:14:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你干什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.16,0:14:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.38,0:15:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.64,0:16:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,住手 你做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.32,0:16:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.65,0:16:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,给我乖一点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.82,0:16:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不想老公丢工作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.36,0:17:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,就听话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.57,0:17:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他这么努力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.71,0:17:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你狠心吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.87,0:17:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,看他没工作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.68,0:17:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我还能帮他升官唷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.38,0:17:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不是坏事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.08,0:17:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,听话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.02,0:17:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,乖一点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.62,0:18:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,爽吧\N不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.29,0:18:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,很爽吧\N住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.58,0:18:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.60,0:19:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,乖一点
