Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.61,0:19:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.48,0:19:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.50,0:19:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,给我舔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.34,0:19:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好好舔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.35,0:20:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好好舔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.34,0:21:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.37,0:21:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好好舔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.18,0:21:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,好好舔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.84,0:23:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.04,0:23:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,再来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.55,0:24:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.55,0:24:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,乖一点
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.77,0:24:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.81,0:25:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.76,0:25:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.67,0:25:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.91,0:25:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,饶了我
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.02,0:25:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.72,0:26:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
