Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.19,0:26:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.10,0:27:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.70,0:27:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,很爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.38,0:27:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.43,0:29:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.91,0:30:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.51,0:31:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,快动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.78,0:31:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.22,0:31:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,快一点
