Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.87,0:39:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,舔干净
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.76,0:40:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.96,0:42:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,其实很爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.18,0:42:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.98,0:42:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.51,0:43:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.64,0:45:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我会守约
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.22,0:45:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,让你老公升官
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.82,0:45:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你乖乖配合
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.36,0:48:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.33,0:48:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.93,0:48:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么不穿衣服？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.07,0:48:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,因为有个大事唷
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.57,0:48:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我被任命为开发部长
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.95,0:48:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.75,0:48:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,多亏你了 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.80,0:49:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,-4月2日-
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.62,0:49:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.52,0:49:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.70,0:49:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,没有话要讲吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.10,0:49:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.67,0:49:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你老公没讲吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.08,0:50:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他只有讲工作的事
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.75,0:50:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,说过了吧 我会守约
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.65,0:50:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.26,0:50:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,真见外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.16,0:50:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,展现你的诚意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.34,0:50:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.94,0:50:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.73,0:50:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好好表示诚意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.02,0:51:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,住手\N说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.52,0:51:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我说过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.86,0:51:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,大太
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.08,0:51:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,身材不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.90,0:52:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.40,0:52:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.02,0:52:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,听话
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.76,0:52:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,太太
